# Agent Interface

Defines the Agent interface and BuildContext for code generation agents.

## Agent Interface

```
interface Agent:
    Build(ctx, buildCtx: BuildContext) -> list of strings, error
    Validate(ctx, validation: Validation, generatedFiles: list of strings) -> boolean, string, error
    GetName() -> string
    GetType() -> string
```

### BuildContext

```
BuildContext:
    Intent: Intent
    Validations: list of ValidationFile
    ProjectRoot: string
    OutputDir: string
    GenerationID: string
    DependencyNames: list of strings
    ProjectIntent: Intent
```

## CLIAgent (Base Implementation)

Generic CLI agent wrapping any command-line tool. Constructs prompts, pipes to command, detects files.

## MockAgent

Mock implementation for testing. Records calls, returns configurable responses.
